#
# 3) Covariate matrix (1024 × 6)
#    - Six-dimensional covariate information per spot
#
# 4) Tissue boundary data frame
#    - Boundary information required as input for the spVC method
#
# 5) Tissue cluster label (1024×1)
#    - layer label information required as input for the DESpace method
#
